Que:-Write a php script to change the background color of the browser using a switch
stmt according to the day of the week....
<br>
<html><body>
	<form method="post" action="day_color.php">
	  Enter Day:
	<input type="text"name="t1"><br>
	<input type="submit"value="ok">
	</form>
</body></html>
<?php
$d=$_POST["t1"];
switch($d)
{
  case "Monday":echo("<body bgcolor='red'>");
		break;
  case "Tuesday":echo("<body bgcolor='blue'>");
		break;
  case "Wednesday":echo("<body bgcolor='pink'>");
		break;
  case "Thursday":echo("<body bgcolor='yellow'>");
		break;
  case "Friday":echo("<body bgcolor='green'>");
		break;
  case "Saturday":echo("<body bgcolor='Black'>");
		break;
  case "Sunday":echo("<body bgcolor='purple'>");
		break;
  }
?>

Output:-
